Package: NCmisc
Type: Package
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-07-25
Title: Miscellaneous general purpose functions
Author: Nicholas Cooper
Maintainer: Nicholas Cooper <nick.cooper@cimr.cam.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 2.10), grDevices, graphics, stats, utils
Suggests: proftools
Description: A set of handy functions. Includes: versatile one line progress bar, one 
 line function timer with detailed output, time delay function, text histogram, CRAN
 package search, simpler package installer, Linux command install check, a flexible 
 Mode function, and more
License: GPL (>= 2)